  <steps>
    <step num="0">Add oats, walnuts and ground almonds to a large bowl and mix together. </step>
    <step num="1">Add peanut butter, honey and cinnamon and mix. </step>
    <step num="2">Add carrot and raisins to the mixture and mix until a everything has stuck together. </step>
    <step num="3">Form into 12 balls and place on baking paper. </step>
    <step num="4">Refrigerate for 1 hour. </step>
    <step num="5">Enjoy! </step>
  </steps>
